_:Nb8a0092da55146348023e4f08a53b6ce <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Tara Smith is the Chief Operating Officer at the Home Office.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to joining the Home Office Tara served as Chief Operating Officer at the Department for Business and Trade from May 2023 until 27 April 2026.</p>\n\n<p>Tara has also worked as the Director of People and Resources at the Food Standards Agency and as the Strategic Finance Director at the Department for Work and Pensions.</p>\n\n<p>She is a chartered accountant and started her career with PwC. She worked in Ireland, Canada and the UK for more than 10 years before joining the civil service in 2006.</p>\n\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
